# Documentation sync

- **Source of truth**: `app/main.py`, `app/model.py`, `Dockerfile`, and `docker-compose.yml`.
- **Docs**: English only under [`doc/`](/doc); update the relevant pages (`api.md`, `deployment.md`, `configuration.md`, `architecture.md`) when behavior or contracts change.
- **README**: Preserve a prominent link to [`doc/README.md`](doc/README.md); avoid duplicating long API tables only in README if `doc/api.md` is the canonical reference.
- When unsure, load the personal Agent Skill **technical-docs-sync** (`~/.cursor/skills/technical-docs-sync/SKILL.md`) for workflow and checklists.
